en.about_message:
I want to thank everyone who helped me developing this bot during the years: le laide, Ganjalf, umbit, all the users who gave me feedback and helped me during the years.
Sasha has been online as a userbot from 2016/02/15 since 2020/01/18, and as a bot since 2016/09/27.

@AISashaBot is written in Python3 using @Pyrogram and peewee, it runs on a Raspberry Pi 3 and it is developed by @EricSolinas.

